category: Text
requires: perl
sdesc: "Converts DocBook XML to OpenDocument"
ldesc: "Docbook2odf is a toolkit that automaticaly converts DocBook XML 
to OASIS OpenDocument (ODF, the ISO standardized format used for texts, 
spreadsheets and presentations). Conversion is based on a XSLT which 
makes it easy to convert DocBook->ODF, ODT, ODS and ODP as all these 
documents are XML based."
